ta.3442"><date>2009-03-20</date><respStmt><name>IDP</name></respStmt><item>Crosswalked to EpiDoc XML</item></change></revisionDesc></teiHeader><text><body><head lang="en"><date>161BC</date>
<placeName cert="high" full="yes">Memphis</placeName></head><div type="edition" lang="grc" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><ab part="N">
    <lb n="1"/>Σαραπίωνι τῶν διαδόχων καὶ ὑποδιοικητῆι 

    <lb n="2"/>παρὰ Πτολεμαίου Μακεδόνος τοῦ ὄντος 

    <lb n="3"/>ἐν κατοχῆι ἐν τῶι μεγάλωι Σαραπιείωι 

    <lb n="4"/>τοῦτο ἔτος <num value="11">ια</num> καὶ τῶν διδυμῶν. ἐντυχόντων 

    <lb n="5"/>ἡμῶν σοι ἔτι πρότερον ὑπὲρ τῶν ὀφειλομένων 

    <lb n="6"/>πρὸς τὴν σύνταξιν τοῦ <num value="18">ιη</num> <expan><ex cert="high">ἔτους</ex></expan> ἐκ τοῦ Σαραπιείου 

    <lb n="7"/>ὀλυρῶν <expan><ex cert="high">ἀρταβῶν</ex></expan> <num value="160">ρξ</num>, ἀφ᾽ ὧν δεδόσθαι μηνῶν <num value="6">ϛ</num>, <del rend="erasure" status="unremarkable">κκαὶ</del> 

    <lb n="8"/>εἰς δὲ τὸ <num value="19">ιθ</num> <expan><ex cert="high">ἑξα</ex>μή<ex cert="high">νου</ex></expan> <add place="supralinear">εἰς δὲ <supplied reason="omitted" cert="high">τὸ</supplied></add> <num value="20">κ</num> <expan><ex cert="high">ἔτος</ex></expan> μηθὲν εἰληφέναι, συνέταξα 

    <lb n="9"/>καθ᾽ ἣν ἔχεις εἰς τὸ θεῖον εὐσέβειαν ἀποδοῦναι, 

    <lb n="10"/>ὅθεν καὶ γράψαι Με<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ν</supplied>νίδην τὸν ἐπιμελητὴν 

    <lb n="11"/>Ψινταῆτι ἀποδοῦναι τά τε προγεγραμ-

    <lb n="12"/>μένα, ὁμοίως δὲ καὶ τὴν γινομένην 
  
    <lb n="13"/>ἐκ τοῦ Ἀσκληπιείου καὶ εἰς τὸ λοιπὸν <choice><corr>εὐτακτ<supplied reason="omitted" cert="high">εῖν, ὅπ</supplied>ως</corr><sic>ευτακτως</sic></choice> 

    <lb n="14"/>ἀπαρτιζώμεθα ἀκολούθως τοῖς ἐπὶ τῶν τοιούτων 

    <lb n="15"/>ὑποκειμένοις. ἐπεὶ οὖν οὐδὲ ὥς <supplied reason="omitted" cert="high">ἕως</supplied> τοῦ νῦν 

    <lb n="16"/>γέγονεν ἡμῖν ἡ ἀπόδοσις, τόν τε βασιλέα 

    <lb n="17"/>πλειονάκις δι᾽ ἐντεύξεως παρηνωχλήκαμεν, 

    <lb n="18"/>ἔτι δὲ καὶ τὸν φεριτ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ὸ</supplied>β καὶ σέ, συστήσαντός σοι 

    <lb n="19"/>τὸ παρ᾽ ἡμῶν παιδάριον ἐν τῶι ἱερῶι, 

    <lb n="20"/>ἀξιοῦμέν σε καὶ ἐν τούτοις ἡμῖν συνεργή-

    <lb n="21"/>σαντα συντάξαι ἐπιστρεφέστερον <supplied reason="omitted" cert="high">τῶι Ψινταῆτι</supplied> ἀπο-

    <lb n="22"/>δοῦναι ἡμῖν τὰ προγεγραμμένα, ὅπως 

    <lb n="23"/>δυνώμεθα τὰς ἐν τῶι ἱερῶι λειτουργίας ἐπιτελεῖν, 

    <lb n="24"/>ἀνακαλέσασθαι δὲ Ἀμ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ῶ</supplied>σιν τὸν διαδεχόμενον αὐτὸν, 

    <lb n="25"/>ὅπως ἀπροφάσιστα ἦι. εὐτύχει. </ab></div><div n="meta.3442" type="description" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><rs type="material" cert="high">Papyrus</rs></p></div><div n="meta.3442" type="commentary" subtype="textDate" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><date type="textDate" notBefore="-0161-01-10">nach 10. Jan. 161 v.Chr.</date></p></div><div n="meta.3442" type="commentary" subtype="mentionedDates" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><head>Erwähnte Daten</head><p>Z. 6: <date type="mentioned" notBefore="-0164" notAfter="-0163">164 - 163 v.Chr.</date></p><p>Z. 8: <date type="mentioned" notBefore="-0163" notAfter="-0162">163 - 162 v.Chr.</date></p></div><div n="meta.3442" type="bibliography" subtype="principalEdition" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><listBibl default="NO"><bibl type="publication" subtype="principal" default="NO"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">UPZ</title><biblScope type="volume">1</biblScope><biblScope type="numbers">51</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="Trismegistos" default="NO"><biblScope type="numbers">3442</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="DDbDP" default="NO"><series>0245</series>; <biblScope type="volume">1</biblScope>; <biblScope type="numbers">51</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref type="Perseus" href="0245;1;51" evaluate="all" from="ROOT" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.3442" type="bibliography" subtype="corrections" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><head>BL-Einträge nach BL-Konkordanz</head><bibl type="BL" default="NO"><biblScope type="volume">IX</biblScope>, S. <biblScope type="pages">362</biblScope></bibl></div><div n="meta.3442" type="bibliography" subtype="illustrations" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p>keine</p></div><div n="meta.3442" type="history" subtype="locations" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><placeName type="ancientFindspot" cert="high" full="yes">Memphis</placeName></p></div></body></text></TEI